WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Welcome to Operative Six. This course will cover the core pillars of influence and behavioral analysis.

2
00:00:30.000 --> 00:02:00.000
In this course overview, we outline the key topics and the skills you will develop across the training program.

3
